text: Claudia Naomi Webbe (born 8 March 1965) is a British politician. She is the Member of Parliament for Leicester East since 2019. She was suspended from the party whip in September 2020 after being charged with harassment of a woman. She was then removed from the party on 3 November 2021 after being convicted in October 2021. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Labour Party (UK) MPs Category:Politicians from London Category:Independent politicians Category:UK MPs 2019â€“2024 Category:People from Leicester
